WEBVTT

00:01.710 --> 00:05.440
<i>Previously on "Transformers Prime"...</i>

00:05.510 --> 00:08.180
Well, aren't you the clever one?

00:09.280 --> 00:15.020
You shall serve as a constant
reminder to those who dare fail me.

00:16.090 --> 00:17.590
What?!

00:17.660 --> 00:20.460
Three keys are accounted for.

00:23.930 --> 00:27.830
It would seem
I have the run of the place.

00:27.900 --> 00:30.640
Ah, there you are.

00:37.540 --> 00:42.650
The fate of Cybertron now
rests in Starscream's hands...

00:42.720 --> 00:45.550
whatever his intention.

00:45.620 --> 00:49.990
Please pardon my unannounced
visit, Lord Megatron.

00:54.690 --> 00:59.030
But I have come bearing
a peace offering.

01:06.610 --> 01:10.010
Few things of value come
without a price.

01:10.080 --> 01:14.550
So, tell me, Starscream, what is
it that you wish in return?

01:14.610 --> 01:18.120
Only to be a Decepticon once again.

01:18.180 --> 01:21.290
Dreadwing is my
first lieutenant now.

01:21.350 --> 01:25.290
And I accept that much has
changed during my absence.

01:25.360 --> 01:29.600
I only wish to serve
you, my one true master,

01:29.600 --> 01:32.430
in any way that you deem fit.

01:32.500 --> 01:36.400
I am deeply impressed by your
accomplishment, Starscream.

01:36.470 --> 01:41.710
And know that I will put your offerings
to good use, whatever the outcome.

01:41.770 --> 01:46.240
Uh, outcome?
Of what?

01:46.310 --> 01:50.450
See to it that Knockout is
extracted from the wall.

01:55.120 --> 01:58.720
Ah, it's good to be back.

02:02.660 --> 02:09.270
Now, what will we be
fishing for today, my liege?

02:11.640 --> 02:15.740
Starscream's true motives.

